TEXT.HEADLINE: A New Bid to End Texting While Driving
TEXT.SHORT_DESC: For the fifth straight legislative session, Texas lawmakers will consider bills proposing a statewide ban on texting while driving. There’s more momentum than ever to get it passed, but a difference of opinions among the state’s new leadership could stand in its way.
